      "content": "hey, i'm working on a brand strategy for a new ultra-premium luxury watch collection. i need to narrow down our target market. can you help me build out a detailed profile for the \"ideal\" customer for this type of product? like, who are they, what's their background, what do they value? give me a really specific persona profile.",
